I would say the location is fantastic, just a few minutes walk from the beach and the old town. The entire hotel is spotless clean and very well maintained. The hosts are wonderful and kind. Yet for me, the biggest asset of this place is the panoramic 180+ deg view of the port, Sozopol's charming old town, St. Ivan island, and the entire coastline all the way to Cape Emine.
